<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4066.3.6>
    bibo:endPage "310" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "301" ;
    bibo:volume "4066" ;
    dc:creator "Kovačić, Marcelo; Ordines, Francesc; Schliewen, Ulrich K." ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Speleogobius (Teleostei: Gobiidae) from the Western Mediterraenean Sea" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262958>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262961>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262959>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262960>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262962> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262958>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Map showing the sampling stations where the specimens were collected (black dots). Isobaths of 50, 100 and 200 m are also shown. The holotype was collected at the station numbered 9. The paratypes PMR VP 3511, ZSM 43988, PMR VP 3512, PMR VP 3513 and ZSM 43989, and the specimens included as additional material ZSM 43990, ZSM-PIS-GO- 1065 / 1066, ZSM 43991 and ZSM-PIS-GO- 1067 / 1068, were collected from stations numbered 1, 4, 6, 5, 8, 3, 2, 7 and 9, respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262961>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Speleogobius llorisi sp. nov., head LL sensory papillae and canal pores: paratype, PMR VP 3512 (P 54), male, 24.4 + 5.5 mm, Spain, Balearic Islands, Mallorca. Terminology in text. Drawing by M. Kovačić." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262961/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262959>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Speleogobius llorisi sp. nov. Holotype: PMR VP 3510 (P 3), female, 25.6 + 5.6 mm, Spain, Balearic Islands, Mallorca. A: freshly collected specimen; B: preserved specimen. Photos by (A) F. Ordines, (B) M. Kovačić." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262959/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262960>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Speleogobius llorisi sp. nov. Paratype: PMR VP 3512 (P 54), male, 24.4 + 5.5 mm, Spain, Balearic Islands, Mallorca. Preserved specimen. Photo by M. Kovačić." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262960/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262962>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Speleogobius llorisi sp. nov. X-ray of specimen ZSM-PIS-GO- 1067 / 1068, undetermined sex, 21.1 + 4.1 mm, Spain, Balearic Islands, Mallorca. X-ray by Z. Gholami." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262962/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

